restaurantDescription: In the search for a masterfully prepared dining experience? Look no further than your Dedham, Massachusetts Capital Grille. Located at Legacy Place Shopping Mall right off I-95 and US-1, we guarantee to deliver delicious dry-aged steaks and entrees made with the highest quality ingredients. We feature over 350 new and old world wines curated by our Sommelier and classic cocktails with our own twist. Make a reservation at our restaurant on 410 Legacy Place today where an unforgettable experience awaits you.
